18. Industry Tips
Tip 1

Keep state minimal.

Store only necessary data.

Tip 2

Use descriptive names.

✅

const [userName, setUserName]

❌

const [x, setX]
Tip 3

Never mutate state.

Use:

setItems([...items, newItem]);
Tip 4

Group related state logically.

Example:

const [formData, setFormData] =
useState({
  name: "",
  email: ""
});
Tip 5

In real projects, almost every component uses state:

